message.entry: NU and Z must be the same size.
BESSELH no longer returns a second output. Use H = BESSELH(NU,Z) instead.
BESSELI no longer returns a second output. Use I = BESSELI(NU,Z) instead.
BESSELJ no longer returns a second output. Use J = BESSELJ(NU,Z) instead.
BESSELK no longer returns a second output. Use K = BESSELK(NU,Z) instead.
BESSELY no longer returns a second output. Use Y = BESSELY(NU,Z) instead.
BESSELH(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of empty array and non-scalar input.
BESSELI(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of empty array and non-scalar input.
BESSELJ(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of empty array and non-scalar input.
BESSELK(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of empty array and non-scalar input.
BESSELY(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of empty array and non-scalar input.
BESSELH(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of row and column vectors. Use BSXFUN or [NU1 Z1] = MESHGRID(NU, Z); BESSELH(NU1,Z1) instead.
BESSELI(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of row and column vectors. Use BSXFUN or [NU1 Z1] = MESHGRID(NU, Z); BESSELI(NU1,Z1) instead.
BESSELJ(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of row and column vectors. Use BSXFUN or [NU1 Z1] = MESHGRID(NU, Z); BESSELJ(NU1,Z1) instead.
BESSELK(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of row and column vectors. Use BSXFUN or [NU1 Z1] = MESHGRID(NU, Z); BESSELK(NU1,Z1) instead.
BESSELY(NU,Z) no longer accepts mixtures of row and column vectors. Use BSXFUN or [NU1 Z1] = MESHGRID(NU, Z); BESSELY(NU1,Z1) instead.
